{"lemma":"حافَظَ","slug":"حافَظَ","root":"ح.ف.ظ","root_slug":"ح-ف-ظ","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ف-ظ","pos":"V","pos_camel":"verb","paradigm":[{"role":"past_2ms","form":"حافَظْتَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2fs","form":"حافَظْتِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_2md","form":"حافَظْتُما","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_2mp","form":"حافَظْتُم","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_2fp","form":"حافَظْتُنَّ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3ms","form":"حافَظَ","in_corpus":true,"count":17,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3fs","form":"حافَظَت","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"past_3md","form":"حافَظا","in_corpus":true,"count":5,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3fd","form":"حافَظَتا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"past_3mp","form":"حافَظُوا","in_corpus":true,"count":6,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_3fp","form":"حافَظْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2ms","form":"تُحافِظ","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تُحافِظِي","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2fs","form":"تُحافِظِينَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تُحافِظا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2md","form":"تُحافِظانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تُحافِظُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2mp","form":"تُحافِظُونَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_2fp","form":"تُحافِظْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"2","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3ms","form":"يُحافِظ","in_corpus":true,"count":5,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3fs","form":"تُحافِظ","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"s"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يُحافِظا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3md","form":"يُحافِظانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تُحافِظا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3fd","form":"تُحافِظانِ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"d"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يُحافِظُوا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3mp","form":"يُحافِظُونَ","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"present_3fp","form":"يُحافِظْنَ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"3","gen":"f","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1mp","form":"حافَظْنا","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"},{"role":"past_1ms","form":"حافَظْتُ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"p","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1ms","form":"أُحافِظ","in_corpus":true,"count":1,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"s"},{"role":"present_1mp","form":"نُحافِظ","in_corpus":false,"count":null,"asp":"i","per":"1","gen":"m","num":"p"}],"frequency_in_corpus":37,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حافَظَ","root":"حفظ","pos":"N","occurrence_count":13},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["name","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n8508"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B8%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to preserve, to maintain, to keep up, to uphold, to sustain"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to supervise, to control, to watch over, to watch out for"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to take care, to attend, to pay attention"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to keep, to follow, to observe, to comply, to conform"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to protect, to guard, to defend"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"guard, guardian, keeper, custodian, caretaker"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hafiz (one who knows the Qur'an by heart)"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a male given name, Hafez or Hafiz"},{"pos":"name","gloss":"Hafez aš-Šīrāzi, a famous mystic 14th century Persian poet, who also wrote in Arabic and whose poems are sometimes used as omens."}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of حَفِظَ (ḥafiẓa, “to guard, to keep; to memorize”), from the root ح ف ظ (ḥ f ẓ). The Persian poet was named such as he had memorised the Qurʾān."},"ipa":["/ħaː.fa.ðˤa/","/ħaː.fiðˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n8508","headword_ar":"حَافِظٌ","root":"HfZ","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafiyZN","text_ar":"حَفِيظٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Keeping, preserving, guarding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking care of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a keeper, preserver,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeping and tending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturing and defending,"},{"kind":"text","text":"camels or the like; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a keeper and tender"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof: (K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeping"},{"kind":"text","text":"a secret [and an oath]: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"keeping,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retaining,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the Kur-án [&c.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the mind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"memory; knowing"},{"kind":"text","text":"it, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"learning"},{"kind":"text","text":"it,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by heart:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intrusted with a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to keep it, preserve it, guard it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take care of it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"careful, mindful, attentive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"considerate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1:)] and the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a keeper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"person mindful, of the ordinances prescribed by God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd and Jel in l. 31:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafaZapN","text_ar":"حَفَظَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huf~aAZN","text_ar":"حُفَّاظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, K:) the latter pl. particularly applied to persons"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endowed with a faculty of retaining in the mind what they have heard, and seldom forgetting what they learn by heart."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN HafiyZunaA","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ حَفِيظُنَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayokumo","text_ar":"عَلَيْكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfiZunaA","text_ar":"حَافِظُنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is our keeper over you"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) It is said in the S that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafiyZN","text_ar":"حَفِيظٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaAfiZN","text_ar":"مُحَافِظٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [but this seems to be a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfiZN","text_ar":"حَافِظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] and hence (it is there added) the saying in the Kur [vi. 104, and xi. 88], ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamaA A^anaA Ealayokumo biHafiyZK","text_ar":"وَمَا اَنَا عَلَيْكُمْ بِحَفِيظٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And I am not a defender,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a watcher,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as I rather think,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a keeper, over you"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfiZN lidiynihi waA^amaAnatihi wayamiynihi","text_ar":"حَافِظٌ لِدِينِهِ وَاَمَانَتِهِ وَيَمِينِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man who is a keeper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his religion and his deposite and his oath"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafiyZN","text_ar":"حَفِيظٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"likewise: (Msb:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfiZN liyamiynihi","text_ar":"حَافِظٌ لِيَمِينِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who keeps his oath from being used,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered, on,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for, ordinary, mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vile, occasions,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purposes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN HaAfiZu","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ حَافِظُ"},{"kind":"page_break","n":603},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEayoni","text_ar":"العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man whom sleep does not overcome:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, K:) because the eye guards the person when sleep does not overcome it. (TA.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHafiyZu","text_ar":"الحَفِيظُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also a name of God; meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Preserver of all things;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He from whose preservation nothing is excluded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not even a thing of the weight of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ar~ap","text_ar":"ذَرَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the heavens, nor on the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who preserves from oblivion, for,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"against, his creatures and his servants, what they do of good or evil; who preserves the heavens and the earth by his power, and whom the preservation of both does not burden."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHafaZapu","text_ar":"الحَفَظَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is an appellation of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The recording angels, who write down the actions of the sons of Adam,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mankind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaAfiZuwna","text_ar":"الحَافِظُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HafiyZN","text_ar":"حَفِيظٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is sometimes trans.; as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa HafiyZN Eilomaka waEiloma gayorika","text_ar":"هُوَ حَفِيظٌ عِلْمَكَ وَعِلْمَ غَيْرِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He knows by heart thy science, and the science of others beside thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alquw~apu AlHaAfiZapu","text_ar":"القُوَّةُ الحَافِظَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and simply"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaAfiZapu","text_ar":"الحَافِظَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The retentive faculty of the mind; retentiveness of mind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"memory;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHafoZu","text_ar":"الحَفْظُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HifoZu Alqalobi","text_ar":"حِفْظُ القَلْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAfiZN","text_ar":"حَافِظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A distinct and direct road;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(En-Nadr, K, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not one that is apparent at one time and then ceases to be traceable."},{"kind":"text","text":"(En-Nadr, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","Msb","Lh"]}]},"classical_definitions":{"source":"hawramani","url":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AD%D8%A7%D9%81%D8%B8/","headword_ar":"حافظة","entries":[{"lexicon_id":"dictionary_18","lexicon_en":"Al-Sharīf al-Jurjānī, Kitāb al-Taʿrīfāt (d. 1413 CE)","lexicon_ar":"كتاب التعريفات للشريف الجرجاني","permalink":"https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=23203#1d9121","body_html":"<span>الحافظة: هي قوة محلها التجويف الأخير من الدماغ؛ من شأنها حفظ ما يدركه الوهم من المعاني الجزئية، فهي خزانة للوهم، كالخيال للحس المشترك.</span>"}]}}